###################### AUTO SCALLING #####################
Test Auto Scaling
Run inside EC2:
sudo yum install -y stress
stress --cpu 2 --timeout 300
1. Install stress
sudo yum install -y stress
2. Run CPU load
After 1–2 minutes:
CloudWatch detects:
CPUUtilization > 70%
Then:
 Scale OUT triggers
    • ASG increases instances 
    • Example:
Before: 2 instances
After: 3 instances
After 5 minutes (timeout ends)
CPU drops
Then:
CloudWatch detects:
CPUUtilization < 20%
Scale IN triggers
    • Instance count reduces 
    • Example: 
3 → 2 instances
