I reused the default VPC and subnets
4. Security Group
it decides:
Who can come IN
What can go OUT
1. Ingress (Incoming Traffic)
Ingress = traffic coming INTO your server
{
cidr_blocks = ["0.0.0.0/0"]
}
 Means:
    • Anyone from internet can access your app on port 8080 
Egress (Outgoing Traffic)
Egress = traffic going OUT from your server
cidr_blocks = ["0.0.0.0/0"]
}
 Means:
    • Your server can connect to anywhere (internet) 
Port	Purpose
80	Load Balancer traffic
